These points were explicitly appreciated:
- The **hands-on format** is valuable
- Letting participants **change parameters and run code** works well
- The workshop gives **good insight into models and parameter comparison**
- The **notebooks are generally well organized**
- **Transfer learning explanation** was considered helpful
- **Grad-CAM results** were seen as impressive
- **Font size/readability** was good
- Google Colab as environment was appreciated

